body:
@johnclary there are a few labels that need to be amended for Shared Mobility/Smart Mobility. 

I've already changed the Product label from SMO to Smart Mobility Reporting Tracker. 

I'm proposing that we change "Workgroup: SM" to "Workgroup: Shared Mobility Services," and create a new label "Workgroup: Smart Mobility."

During the sprint review on August 26th, Andrea pointed out the need for a comments section. 

In the spreadsheet that the SM team is using to track Provider information, she is adding a note if providers haven't paid or if something doesn't match. Staff would like to have that functionality for payment information in the app.

@dianamartin indicated we would be able to do this.

